title: Proposal of Burning Most of the MGP Held by The Team
body:
Dear community, 

After the calculation and discussion, we found  that the team holds too high a ratio of MGP and we plan transfer the vast majority of the team's holdings to theNull Address: 0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000dead

We’ll only retain the contract address below for regular airdrop program and project development & operations. 
Contract address: 0xd9746d12d9f8bce10b2a2960275edb378ff69a08

We intend to effectively enhance the decentralization of the Magic Cube project by the above actions.
author: 0xAaE580038D7922e59b4C3eBCe5A6Ee6032168D01
